  "body": "**Do you want to request a *feature* or report a *bug*?**\r\nBug\r\n\r\n**What is the current behavior?**\r\nTextarea doesn't update when getting new value\r\neg:\r\n```jsx\r\nrender() {\r\n  return (\r\n    <div>\r\n      <textarea>{this.state.value}</textarea>\r\n      <input type=\"text\" value={this.state.value} />\r\n      <span>{this.state.value}</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n  );\r\n}\r\n```\r\nIf the state updates, input will update, span will update, but you can't see any changes on textarea\r\n\r\n[JS Fiddle](https://jsfiddle.net/69z2wepo/193493/)\r\n\r\n**What is the expected behavior?**\r\nTextarea should render the updated value\r\n\r\n**Which versions of React, and which browser / OS are affected by this issue? Did this work in previous versions of React?**\r\n\r\nReact 16.4.1\r\nFirefox 59.0.2\r\nChrome 66.0.3359.181  64 bits\r\nMac os High Sierra 10.13.4\r\n",
